            <title>[CASSANDRA-17708] Fix flaky testOutboundConnectionsAreRejectedWhenAuthFails</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17708</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;testOutboundConnectionsAreRejectedWhenAuthFails was introduced in&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17661&quot; title=&quot;Adding support to perform certificate based internode authentication&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17661&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17661&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems it was introduced flaky from the very beginning as per this run in a loop - &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra?branch=flaky-testOutboundConnectionsAreRejectedWhenAuthFails&amp;amp;filter=all&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra?branch=flaky-testOutboundConnectionsAreRejectedWhenAuthFails&amp;amp;filter=all&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CC &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=janaki.manchala&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;janaki.manchala&quot;&gt;janaki.manchala&lt;/a&gt; , &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jonmeredith&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jonmeredith&quot;&gt;jonmeredith&lt;/a&gt;, &#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ycai&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ycai&quot;&gt;ycai&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

