&lt;p&gt;The patch only contains test code changes. The flaky tests do not fail in the run attached. And &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/jyothsnakonisa/cassandra/132/workflows/182dd59d-cffe-4f6e-959e-0c32395b9088/jobs/2017/steps&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;running it repeatedly&lt;/a&gt; (500 times) also shows green. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
